data.text:
The duo Blue Sky Black Death consists of producers Kingston and Young God, who produce the entire project, while Holocaust (a Wu-Tang Clan affiliate, also known as Warcloud) provides all vocals. The album’s lead single is “The Ocean”, which features “No Image” as it’s B-Side. Due to a fan petition to Babygrande Records, the album’s instrumentals were released on June 24, 2008. As of November 6, 2008 the album has moved 4,185 units
